			"type": "therapy",
			"content": {
				"number": "2",
				"title": "F√∂rslag till intraven√∂s antibiotikabehandling vid akut bakteriell meningit",
				"id": "",
				"text": "<table width=\"671\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"186\">\r\n<p><strong>Bakgrund/<br />bakterie</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"120\">\r\n<p><strong>Antibiotika</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"121\">\r\n<p><strong>Dosering vuxna</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"112\">\r\n<p><strong>Dosering<br /> barn</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"132\">\r\n<p><strong>Behandlings-<br />tid</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"186\">\r\n<p>Inledande <br />behandling<sup>a</sup></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"120\">\r\n<p>cefotaxim +<br /> ampicillin<sup>b</sup></p>\r\n<p><em>alternativt</em></p>\r\n<p>meropenem</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"121\">\r\n<p>3 g x 4</p>\r\n<p>3 g x 4</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>2 g x 3</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"112\">\r\n<p>50&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;4<br />50&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;4</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>40&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;3</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"132\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"186\">\r\n<p>Vid <em>allvarlig &ouml;verk&auml;nslighet</em><sup>c <br /></sup>mot betalaktam-antibiotika <sup>d</sup></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"120\">\r\n<p>moxifloxacin +<br />vancomycin</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"121\">\r\n<p>400&nbsp;mg&nbsp;x&nbsp;1</p>\r\n<p>1 g x 3</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"112\">\r\n<p>20&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;1</p>\r\n<p>20&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;2</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"132\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"186\">\r\n<p><em>Streptococcus pneumoniae</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"120\">\r\n<p>bensylpenicillin</p>\r\n<p><em>alternativt</em></p>\r\n<p>cefotaxim</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"121\">\r\n<p>3 g x 4</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>3 g x 4</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"112\">\r\n<p>50&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;4</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>50&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;4</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"132\">\r\n<p>10&ndash;14 dagar</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"186\">\r\n<p><em>Neisseria meningitidis</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"120\">\r\n<p>bensylpenicillin</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"121\">\r\n<p>3 g x 4</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"112\">\r\n<p>50&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;4</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"132\">\r\n<p>7 dagar</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"186\">\r\n<p><em>Haemophilus influenzae</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"120\">\r\n<p>cefotaxim</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"121\">\r\n<p>3 g x 4</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"112\">\r\n<p>50&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;4</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"132\">\r\n<p>10&ndash;14 dagar</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"186\">\r\n<p><em>Staphylococcus aureus</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"120\">\r\n<p>cefuroxim</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"121\">\r\n<p>3 g x 4</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"112\">\r\n<p>50&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;4</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"132\">\r\n<p>14&ndash;21 dagar</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"186\">\r\n<p><em>Listeria monocytogenes</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"120\">\r\n<p>ampicillin</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"121\">\r\n<p>3 g x 4</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"112\">\r\n<p>50&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;4</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"132\">\r\n<p>14&ndash;21 dagar</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"186\">\r\n<p><em>Escherichia coli/<br /> Klebsiella pneumoniae</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"120\">\r\n<p>cefotaxim</p>\r\n<p><em>alternativt</em></p>\r\n<p>meropenem</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"121\">\r\n<p>3 g x 4</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>2 g x 3</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"112\">\r\n<p>50&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;4</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>40&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;3</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td width=\"132\">\r\n<p>14&ndash;21 dagar</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"5\" width=\"671\">\r\n<p>a. Vid l&aring;ng transportv&auml;g (&gt;&nbsp;30 min) kan prehospital antibiotikabehandling &ouml;verv&auml;gas (cefotaxim 3&nbsp;g alternativt ceftriaxon 4&nbsp;g)</p>\r\n<p>b. Till&auml;gg av ampicillin till cefotaxim till barn &lt; 3 m&aring;n, till patienter &gt; 15 &aring;r samt till immunsupprimerade individer f&ouml;r att &auml;ven t&auml;cka <em>L. monocytogenes</em></p>\r\n<p>c. Allvarlig &ouml;verk&auml;nslighet inneb&auml;r angio&ouml;dem, luftv&auml;gsobstruktivitet eller anafylaktisk chock</p>\r\n<p>d. Vid risk f&ouml;r <em>L. monocytogenes</em> (enligt b) ges &auml;ven trimetoprim-sufametoxazol (Eusaprim koncentrat till infusionsv&auml;tska, l&ouml;sning 16 mg/ml + 80 mg/ml) 20 ml x 2 intraven&ouml;st till vuxen (barn 0,375 ml/kg kroppsvikt x 2 intraven&ouml;st)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>"
			},
