			"content": {
				"number": "3",
				"title": "F√∂rslag till intraven√∂s antibiotikabehandling vid nekrotiserande mjukdelsinfektioner",
				"id": "",
				"text": "<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td><strong>Preparat</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>Dosering vuxna</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>Dosering barn</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Initial empirisk behandling</strong></td>\r\n<td>meropenem&nbsp;+<br /> klindamycin&nbsp;+<br />ev.&nbsp;tobramycin/gentamicin</td>\r\n<td>1&nbsp;g&nbsp;x&nbsp;3<br />600&nbsp;mg&nbsp;x&nbsp;3<br />5&ndash;7&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;1</td>\r\n<td>20&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;3<br />15&nbsp;mg/kg x&nbsp;3<br />5&ndash;7&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;1</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Vid streptokocker grupp A</strong><sup>a</sup></td>\r\n<td>bensylpenicillin&nbsp;+<br />klindamycin</td>\r\n<td>3&nbsp;g&nbsp;x&nbsp;4<br />600&nbsp;mg&nbsp;x&nbsp;3</td>\r\n<td>50&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;4<br />15&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;3</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Vid fekal blandflora</strong></td>\r\n<td>meropenem<br />ev.&nbsp;tobramycin/gentamicin</td>\r\n<td>1&nbsp;g&nbsp;x&nbsp;3<br />5&ndash;7&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;1</td>\r\n<td>20&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;3<br />5&ndash;7&nbsp;mg/kg&nbsp;x&nbsp;1</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"4\"><sup>a</sup> Vid misst&auml;nkt/verifierad infektion med grupp A-streptokocker kan till&auml;ggsbehandling med intraven&ouml;st immunglobulin &ouml;verv&auml;gas.<br /><br /> Dosering: 1&nbsp;g/kg x 1 (max 50 g) dag 1, d&auml;refter 0,5&nbsp;g/kg (max 25&nbsp;g) x 1 dag 2 och dag&nbsp;3</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><br /><br /></p>"
